#: apps/web/templates/web/profile.html:103
msgid ""
"Get a copy of all the personal data we hold about you, as a JSON file (GDPR "
"right to data portability, Art. 20). No card or payment details are stored."
msgstr ""
"Obține o copie a tuturor datelor personale pe care le deținem despre tine, "
